    {{>guest_header}}
    <div class="main-content maxWidth80 mediaMarginLeft10">
        <div class="aboutPageTitle">About Tradegen</div>
        <div class="aboutPageContent">
            <p>
                Tradegen is a decentralized platform that lets users invest in tokenized strategies developed by other users. 
            </p>
            <p>
                Each strategy has a pool that users can contribute to in exchange for tokens that represent their stake in the pool.
                An on-chain trading bot trades synthetic versions of popular assets using the funds in the pool, and distributes profits
                to users proportional to how many tokens they own.   
            </p>
            <p>
                This lets users algo trade without having to write code or make trades on traditional markets, while enjoying the benefits of blockchain technology. Since the trading
                bots run on-chain, all backtest results and transactions are tamper-proof and publicly verifiable. 
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="aboutPageSubtitle">Our Vision</div>
        <div class="aboutPageContent">
            <p>
                Tradegen's goal is to make the markets more accessible by democratizing algo trading.
                Through blockchain technology and social trading, we aim to provide a fair and transparent platform where anyone has a chance to build prosperity.
                We envision an inclusive community-owned platform where users have an equal opportunity to explore the markets and monetize their insights.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="aboutPageSubtitle">Platform</div>
        <div class="aboutPageContent">
            <p>Some key features of the Tradegen platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    a fungible token on the Celo blockchain (TGEN)
                </li>
                <li>
                    a wallet-based login system
                </li>
                <li>
                    no-code strategy builder that lets users build a wide range of strategies
                </li>
                <li>
                    marketplace where users can sell tokens of strategies they invested in
                </li>
                <li>
                    an incentivized voting system for new strategies
                </li>
                <li>
                    historical performance of strategies and their tokens
                </li>
                <li>
                    code-generation script that builds a ready-to-use trading bot when users build a strategy
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="aboutPageSubtitle">Roadmap</div>
        <div class="aboutPageContent">
            <p>
                We'll be releasing many features throughout 2021/2022 in a series of phases. 
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="extraWeight">Phase 1:</a> market building
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    a more generalized strategy builder for crypto strategies
                </li>
                <li>
                    wider range of strategies and user pools
                </li>
                <li>
                    Ubeswap listing and liquidity mining
                </li>
                <li>
                    custom backtests
                </li>
                <li>
                    improvements to UI and more robust charts
                </li>
                <li>
                    more indicators/comparators as more users join the platform
                </li>
                <li>
                    launch of SDK for creating custom trading bots
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <a class="extraWeight">Phase 2:</a> new asset classes, more tradable assets, and further customization
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    launch of a Synthetix fork and Ubeswap listing for synthetic assets
                </li>
                <li>
                    more tradable assets once Chainlink adds support for Celo
                </li>
                <li>
                    support for custom Chainlink APIs, leading to more indicators/comparators
                </li>
                <li>
                    tokenized index funds representing collections of strategies
                </li>
                <li>
                    tokenized portfolios 
                </li>
                <li>
                    Ubeswap listing for strategy tokens so they can be tradable throughout the Celo ecosystem
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <a class="extraWeight">Phase 3:</a> creating a gamified experience and improving accessibility
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    launch of a prediction market
                </li>
                <li>
                    variety of leaderboards and competitions
                </li>
                <li>
                    iOS and Android apps
                </li>
                <li>
                    ability to chat with other users and interact with posts
                </li>
                <li>
                    'education center' where users are incentivized to write articles on crypto or trading in general
                </li>
                <li>
                    UI for creating custom trading bots and building custom indicators/comparators
                </li>
                <li>
                    'Alpha mining' feature where users can earn TGEN for finding combinations of strategy parameters that outperform the market
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <a class="extraWeight">Phase 4:</a> transition to decentralized autonomous organization (DAO)
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    ability for users to submit proposals for improving the platform and vote on proposals
                </li>
                <li>
                    appointing of new developers and community managers through voting
                </li>
                <li>
                    users can vote on updates to existing strategies
                </li>
                <li>
                    voting system for new indicators/comparators
                </li>
                <li>
                    wrapped versions of TGEN token
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
